{"tid":1044364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【休班警】休班警駕電單車大埔撼欄　拋飛10米外身亡","createTime":"2019-03-02T22:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T08:37:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":302,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"c82ae38424ecaf6a0ff31ef83a4869f24954881f","tid":1044364,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:16:07.000Z","msg":"休班警駕電單車大埔撼欄 拋飛10米外身亡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/mobile/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7c6f3db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/mobile/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔有休班警駕鐵騎自炒喪命。昨日（2日）晚上11時許，一名33歲休班警員駕駛本田CB1000R大馬力電單車，沿大埔太和路支路往吐露港公路行駛，途經右彎位時，突然失控猛撞向路旁防撞欄，他登時人車分離，被拋至欄外倒地，電單車繼續向前滑行10多米翻側。<br />\n<br />\n途經駕駛人士報警，亦有熱心人落車查看休班警員情況，當時他已受重傷，陷入昏迷，稍後由救護員到場將他送院搶後，惜證實不治。新界北總區交通部特別調查隊正調查意外原因，並檢走電單車車Cam了解事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料，涉事電單車於2011年出廠並同年在運輸署首次登記，當年車價約11萬餘元，登記車主姓黃，報住屯門美樂花園。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/photo/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190303052817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190303052817&h=3965f623&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"332bf69e47e7d2907200eb523f0d569cadd9383b","tid":1044364,"uid":140769,"like":37,"dislike":112,"score":-75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:16:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"445d15c7913f668d036586142eda81e88fcc6571","tid":1044364,"uid":140769,"like":25,"dislike":11,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:17:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45512a05c8885cb490988614bf7d6c73837d2ff3","tid":1044364,"uid":25858,"like":65,"dislike":11,"score":